window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Dragons are almost extinct.</b></p> <p>Eggs are rare. The dragons alive are in danger.</p> <p><b>All because of one man.</b></p> <p>Thad Reinhart doesn’t just want dragonriders gone because their role as adjudicators threatens his businesses. His grudge is personal. But there’s one thing he didn’t anticipate.</p> <p><b>S. Beaufont isn’t like any dragonrider before.</b></p> <p>She is modern. She thinks differently. And she definitely doesn’t look like a dragonrider. And when it comes to tackling challenges, Sophia uses new world thinking for old world problems.</p> <p><b>Will it be enough to beat an evil bent on destroying the planet?</b></p> <p>Continue the adventure and find out if Sophia and the Elite can save the dragon population.</p>"; 
